The bounties will be paid within 30 days after the end of the Token Sale.  The total allocation of bounty is 250,000 tokens issued  General Terms:  1|The bounty campaigns starts at the moment of creation of thread on Bitcointalk. 2|250,000 is allocated to the bounty, the amount of rewards will depend on the token sale results. 3|The Bounty Manager can make slight changes in the Bounty Campaign if deemed necessary. 4| Using multi-accounts, cheating, using someone else to do the work and spamming or any kind of unethical behavior when participating to one of the campaigns are not allowed and will get you disqualified from all bounties.  FACEBOOK FOLLOW & REPOSTS  You must like and repost news from our official page within 5 days after their publication and not later, and do not delete them until the ICO ends on 2018/09/30. Stakes will be paid depending on friends and followers:  Facebook payment structure:  100 to 249 friends — 20 SLEE stake 250 to 999 friends & followers — SLEE stake From 1000 to 9999 friends & followers — 100 SLEE  stake 10000 friends & followers and more — 200 SLEE stake  Rules:  1| Participants must share and like SLEECOIN posts. 2| Accounts with fake friends/followers will be disqualified. 3| Minimum 5 repost per week, Maximum 2 repost per day. 4| The account must be at least 6 months old. The number of your followers is being fixed at the moment when you connect your account and doesn’t change during the campaign. 5| You must have Jr. Member or higher rank in bitcointalk  How to participate:  1. You retweet news from our official account within 5 days after their publication and not later, and do not delete them until the ICO ends on 2018/09/30. Each retweet will earn you the following amount of stakes:  Twitter payment structure:  2500 to 4499 followers — 20 SLEE stake 4500 to 9499 followers — 40 SLEE stake 9500 to 14999 followers — 100 SLEE stake 15000 to 99999 followers — 150 SLEE stake 100000+ followers — 200 SLEE stake  Rules:  1| Stakes will be paid depending on REAL (as determined by TwitterAudit) followers (at the start of the campaign). 2| Minimum 5 retweets per week, Maximum 2 retweets per day. 3|Your Twitter audit score must be equal to at least 85% and only real followers from the last audit will count. 4|The account must be at least 5 months old. The number of your followers is being fixed at the moment when you connect your account and doesn’t change during the campaign. 5| You must have Jr. Member or higher rank in bitcointalk  How to participate:  1. Fill and submit this bot: http://t.me/sleecoinbot  Rules:  1|Only one reward per Telegram and Bitcointalk user. 2|You must be active in the Telegram group at least once per week. 3|Join our main chat group, inactive users will not receive the airdrop.
